ZH: 我明天要去造访我的朋友。
EN: I'm going to visit my friend tomorrow.

ZH: 他们特地造访了我家。
EN: They made a special visit to my house.

ZH: 妈妈今天去造访奶奶。
EN: Mom is going to visit grandma today.

ZH: 我们计划下个月去造访国外。
EN: We plan to visit abroad next month.

ZH: 你可以来我家造访。
EN: You can come visit me at my house.

ZH: 明天我们一起去造访那个博物馆，好吗？
EN: Shall we go visit that museum together tomorrow?

ZH: 我们都非常期待去造访这个美丽的城市。
EN: We are all very excited to visit this beautiful city.

ZH: 让我们为了祝贺新婚夫妇去造访他们吧。
EN: Let's visit them to congratulate the newlyweds.

ZH: 虽然我很忙，但是我会努力腾出时间去造访你。
EN: Although I'm busy, I'll try to make time to visit you.

ZH: 他是一个友好的人，常常会造访我们的公司。
EN: He is a friendly person who often visits our company.

ZH: 我们经常造访那个寺庙，为家人祈福。
EN: We often visit that temple to pray for our family.

ZH: 他们已经多年没有造访这个小镇了。
EN: They haven't visited this town for many years.

